dc_title_s: Map of Clark County Indiana, from the latest official surveys & records
dc_description_s: Cadastral map showing landowners. Originally printed in 3 sheets. Insets: Geological map of Clark County, Indiana -- Map of Indiana. Includes statistical tables for the county, lists of county officials, references and explanations, and scenes around the county. Scale 1:31,680. 40 chains to the inch. Drawn and compiled by George W. Davis.
dc_publisher_s: Chas. A. McCann & David S. Koons
